thread.title_full: Fast Cover Travel Insurance reviewed by Antoinette

author: Antoinette
title: Antoinette
text:
I always use Fast Cover Travel Insurance when I travel overseas. I find their prices compatible and their terms are clear.
Mary who helped me to decide if it was better to purchase single insurance for my husband and I or multiple trip insurance for our trips this year was really helpful.
Thanks FCT.
